description: The Faucet is BACK!! Drop by the EUS Common Room this Thursday to talk to the current Editor-In-Chief about becoming a contributor!

Plumbers Band Room is officially launched! You can now practice in the EUS common room or rent music equipment to take off campus. All you🫵need to do is become a member in 4 easy steps:
1) Pay a $10 membership fee and $100 deposit (to be returned at the end of the year) 
2) sign the membership contract
3) fill out the PBR membership form
4) start filling out the booking request form!
All links are in the PBR linktree in bio!
Email bandroom@mcgilleus.ca for any questions

The EUS is currently recruiting a VP External for the remainder of the 2024-2025 academic year!! As VP External, you’ll represent the EUS, maintain connections with student organizations, and oversee key committees and delegations!

Interested?? Apply now, link in bio!! Email president@mcgilleus.ca if you have any questions!
